$Id$

BRUTUS is a fast bruteforcer that tries to break in remotely using password
guessing for TELNET, FTP and POP3 (feel free to add support for other protocols
if you want). Login list generation through SMTP vrfy bruteforcing is also 
supported.
It uses Net::Telnet Perl module, included in this package (you can get it also
at your local CPAN mirror).
Written in one night, using one hand (other arm was broken). pHEAR.

FOR EDUCATIONAL PURPOSES ONLY (tm).

